This paper deals with natural language inference and machine learning models, which are typically studied in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of natural language explanations to improve model interpretability and trust, which could fall under the sub-categories of computing and society (cs.CC) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
